creator: Nik Night Arts
descriptionHtml:
Total Domination is the best one for the ones who are used to control everything. Counter Picks and Counter Items, draft simulation 5 vs 5, comments, and many more in one app.

Features:
- The standart database of best counter picks/counter items
- Unique opportunity to modify and comment counter picks/counter items
- Fast-pacing Game Mode for All Pick, Captains Mode (will raise your chances to kill the whole opponent team)
- GM Draft runs the unique counterpicking algorythm
- Counterpicked enemies/teammates indicators in the Game Mode
- Description of all items available in the application
- Material Design

Want to be invincible in your favorite game Dota 2 and have 4k+ MMR? Enjoy playing Wraith King, but usually suffer from subtle Invoker, who makes your Reincarnation a myth with his EMP? Having some doubts about the itembuild during the game? Now it's no more any kind of problem - set up your own rules with app TOTAL DOMINATION for Dota2 and dominate your enemy on the battlefield right now.

The new level of comfort for every Dota player became a reality. The wide, top-guides and pro-players experience relied, counter picks and counter items database gathered in the application.

The app can be used as a manual against specific characters, or in the Game Mode - in that mode the program will offer you the most efficient counter picks and counter items, according to the enemy pick.

By the way, don't take it easy too much, though the app will give you a tangible advantage, training hard and having skillful fingers are the things you can't avoid.

Dominate, domineer, overthrow with Total Domination - worthy Dota 2 assistant!
